#- One such lesser god is §4§lGaston, § §0the warrior-hero that discovered the Holy Chestplates of Protus, and sired the royal line of the Kingdom of Verda. He grants great strength to his loyal worshippers, so that they too may one day become as 
#- large as a barge. There is also §9§lEretos, §0the mystic that discovered the power of the Flame of Starry Wisdom and is said to be meditating to this day in an attempt to become one with the Flame.
